<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>New Order Received</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f9;
      color: #333;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      padding: 40px;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #3498db;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    .order-details {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .order-id {
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .order-items {
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #777;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="container">
    <h1>New Order Received!</h1>
    <p>Hello Team,</p>
    <p>We have received a new order. Please see the details below:</p>

    <div class="order-details">
      <p class="order-id">Order ID: <%= @order.id %></p>
      <p><strong>Customer Name:</strong> <%= @order.client.name %></p>
      <p><strong>Delivery Address:</strong> <%= @order.client.address %></p>
      <p><strong>Phone Number:</strong> <%= @order.client.phone %></p>
    </div>

    <div class="order-items">
        <h3>Item Ordered:</h3>
        <%= @order.dish.name %> - Price: <%= @order.dish.price.to_f %>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>Please ensure to prepare the order and follow up with the delivery details. Thank you for your prompt attention.</p>
      <p>Best Regards, <br> Your Restaurant Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
